{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Node.nodeType","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeType","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document_Object_Model\">Document Object Model</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/baseURI\"><code>baseURI</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/childNodes\"><code>childNodes</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/firstChild\"><code>firstChild</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/isConnected\"><code>isConnected</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/lastChild\"><code>lastChild</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/nextSibling\"><code>nextSibling</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeName\"><code>nodeName</code></a></li><li><em><code>nodeType</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeValue\"><code>nodeValue</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/ownerDocument\"><code>ownerDocument</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/parentElement\"><code>parentElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/parentNode\"><code>parentNode</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/previousSibling\"><code>previousSibling</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/textContent\"><code>textContent</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/appendChild\"><code>appendChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/cloneNode\"><code>cloneNode()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/compareDocumentPosition\"><code>compareDocumentPosition()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/contains\"><code>contains()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/getRootNode\"><code>getRootNode()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/hasChildNodes\"><code>hasChildNodes()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/insertBefore\"><code>insertBefore()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/isDefaultNamespace\"><code>isDefaultNamespace()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/isEqualNode\"><code>isEqualNode()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/isSameNode\"><code>isSameNode()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/isSupported\"><code>isSupported()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupNamespaceURI\"><code>lookupNamespaceURI()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupPrefix\"><code>lookupPrefix()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/normalize\"><code>normalize()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/removeChild\"><code>removeChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/replaceChild\"><code>replaceChild()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for DOM</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AbortController\"><code>AbortController</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AbortSignal\"><code>AbortSignal</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Attr\"><code>Attr</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CDATASection\"><code>CDATASection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CharacterData\"><code>CharacterData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Comment\"><code>Comment</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation\"><code>DOMImplementation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<div id=\"sect2\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<p>只读属性&nbsp;<code><strong>Node.nodeType</strong></code> 表示的是该节点的类型。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"描述","title":"描述","isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>nodeType</code></strong>&nbsp;属性可用来区分不同类型的节点，比如&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\" title=\"元素\"><code>元素</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Text\" title=\"文本\"><code>文本</code></a> 和&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Comment\" title=\"注释\"><code>注释</code></a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>var <var>type</var></em> = <var>node</var>.nodeType;\n</pre>\n\n<p>返回一个整数，其代表的是节点类型。其所有可能的值请参考&nbsp;<a href=\"#节点类型常量\">节点类型常量</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"常量","title":"常量","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"节点类型常量","title":"节点类型常量","isH3":true,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">常量</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">值</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">描述</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>Node.ELEMENT_NODE</code></td>\n   <td><code>1</code></td>\n   <td>一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\" title=\"元素\"><code>元素</code></a> 节点，例如 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/p\"><code>&lt;p&gt;</code></a> 和 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a>。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>Node.TEXT_NODE</code></td>\n   <td><code>3</code></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a> 或者 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Attr\"><code>Attr</code></a> 中实际的&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Text\" title=\"文字\"><code>文字</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>Node.CDATA_SECTION_NODE</code></td>\n   <td><code>4</code></td>\n   <td>一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CDATASection\"><code>CDATASection</code></a>，例如 <code>&lt;!CDATA[[ … ]]&gt;</code>。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>Node.PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION_NODE</code></td>\n   <td><code>7</code></td>\n   <td>一个用于 XML 文档的 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> ，例如&nbsp;<code>&lt;?xml-stylesheet ... ?&gt;</code> 声明。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>Node.COMMENT_NODE</code></td>\n   <td><code>8</code></td>\n   <td>一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Comment\"><code>Comment</code></a> 节点。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>Node.DOCUMENT_NODE</code></td>\n   <td><code>9</code></td>\n   <td>一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a> 节点。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>Node.DOCUMENT_TYPE_NODE</code></td>\n   <td><code>10</code></td>\n   <td>描述文档类型的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code></a> 节点。例如&nbsp;<code>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</code>&nbsp; 就是用于 HTML5 的。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>Node.DOCUMENT_FRAGMENT_NODE</code></td>\n   <td><code>11</code></td>\n   <td>一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a> 节点</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"已弃用的节点类型常量_deprecated_inline()","title":"已弃用的节点类型常量 <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>以下常量已被弃用，请不要使用。</p>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td>常量</td>\n   <td>值</td>\n   <td>描述</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>Node.ATTRIBUTE_NODE</code></td>\n   <td>2</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\" title=\"元素\"><code>元素</code></a> 的耦合<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Attr\" title=\"属性\"><code>属性</code></a> 。在 <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/dom/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"DOM4\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM4</a> 规范里<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a> 接口将不再实现这个元素属性。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>Node.ENTITY_REFERENCE_NODE</code></td>\n   <td>5</td>\n   <td>一个 XML 实体引用节点。 在 <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/dom/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"DOM4\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM4</a> 规范里被移除。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>Node.ENTITY_NODE</code></td>\n   <td>6</td>\n   <td>一个 XML <code>&lt;!ENTITY ...&gt;</code>&nbsp; 节点。 在 <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/dom/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"DOM4\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM4</a> 规范中被移除。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>Node.NOTATION_NODE</code></td>\n   <td>12</td>\n   <td>一个 XML <code>&lt;!NOTATION ...&gt;</code> 节点。 在 <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/dom/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"DOM4\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM4</a> 规范里被移除。</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>","titleAsText":"已弃用的节点类型常量 \n    \n"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"不同的节点类型","title":"不同的节点类型","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nodeType <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> Node<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">DOCUMENT_NODE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\ndocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>doctype<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nodeType <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> Node<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">DOCUMENT_TYPE_NODE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> fragment <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createDocumentFragment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nfragment<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nodeType <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> Node<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">DOCUMENT_FRAGMENT_NODE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> p <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"p\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"很久很久以前...\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nodeType <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> Node<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">ELEMENT_NODE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>firstChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nodeType <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> Node<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">TEXT_NODE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"注释","title":"注释","isH3":true,"content":"<p>该示例会检查 document 下第一个节点是不是注释，如果不是，则会提醒。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> node <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>documentElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>firstChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>node<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nodeType <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> Node<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">COMMENT_NODE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"你应该认真编写代码注释！\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"specification","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#ref-for-dom-node-nodetype①","title":"DOM Standard"}],"query":"api.Node.nodeType"}}],"toc":[{"text":"描述","id":"描述"},{"text":"语法","id":"syntax"},{"text":"常量","id":"常量"},{"text":"例子","id":"example"},{"text":"规范","id":"specification"}],"summary":"只读属性 Node.nodeType 表示的是该节点的类型。","popularity":0.0006,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.nodeType","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Node.nodeType","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.nodeType","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.nodeType","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Node.nodeType","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.nodeType","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/node/nodetype","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/node/nodetype/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node","title":"Node"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeType","title":"Node.nodeType"}],"pageTitle":"Node.nodeType - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}